Quote:  Each shearing season, for many years he came ... to be `boss of the shearing board'.<i>Ibid.</i> 42  Joe Ferris was head shepherd and Chris Mccauley and Jimmy Muir paddock shepherds, and Bukkie Cordie, packie. ... Murdock McKay was still boss of the shearing board. <i>Ibid.</i> 56 ... sometimes he was heard to be talking to ... the boss of the board Mr McKay.
